@Lissa - Did you get a chance to read anything before the lynch?<br>
@Thesp - Im not too sure Flubber kills massive when that was one of the only people defending him.  Granted its foolish to think of him as a solid town read here, but not overly bad.  You are reading both emo and Flubber as scum though it would seem?<br>
